<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="The_tm_package">The <code>tm</code> package</span></h2>
<p>If using the <code>tm</code> package to count the number of reviews containing the word "perfect", be aware that DocumentTermMatrix lowercases all words by default. To make it case-sensitive, you can set the tolower option to FALSE:</p>
<pre>
dtm &lt;- DocumentTermMatrix(corpus, list(dictionary = word.list, tolower = FALSE))
</pre>
<p>There is more information in <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/ml-classification/discussions/hTm_je6KEeWkUAr_DMJ5Lw">this thread</a>.</p>

